      Nam libero tempore, cum soluta nobis est eligendi optio cumque nihil impedit quo minus id quod maxime placeat facere possimus, omnis voluptas assumenda est, omnis dolor repellendus.
    .categories
      - PagesController::CATEGORY.each do |_, category_name| 
        .category 
          != category_name
  .tiles-container
    .tiles-column.js-sticky-sidebar
      .tile-container.tile-container-lg
        .tile{ style: "background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #11111100, #11111133), url(#{asset_url('samples/home/whatwedo/card1.png')})" }
